{"tid":826153,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"北京大學讀書　馬浚偉1個微博吸7百萬點擊","createTime":"2018-09-18T04:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T03:48:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":29,"dislike":546,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"53415ea9f1ac277b48e67a8d99e1d08bd1a62b11","tid":826153,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/125349_46743861367c23d7b096e3121d780da8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F125349_46743861367c23d7b096e3121d780da8.png&h=0ada6569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/125354_ebd2525e05b455070932e41991c17df4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F125354_ebd2525e05b455070932e41991c17df4.png&h=419a089c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藝人馬浚偉成功報讀北京大學的EMBA課程，近日他飛到北京開學，對重返學校充滿憧憬的他開心表示：「去報到時入咗校務處，佢哋搵人帶我周圍行吓，熟習吓校園環境。其實我今日現身時學校唔係好多人，但遇到嗰女仔佢主動叫我，後嚟佢知我想買校徽同心口針，竟然買嚟送畀我，真係好窩心。」 <br />\n<br />\n而一連數天他要參加學校的活動營，然後才正式開學。談到日前特意準備了校服及文具，他笑謂：「我上咗一條微博關於開學，點擊達七百幾萬，搞到學校都有留意，問我使唔使要啲乜嘢特別安排，因擔心混亂呀，不過我就話唔使嘞，當我普通學生就得。」雖然人不在香港，但馬浚偉亦有留意香港受強颱風吹襲，且表示：「希望唔好有乜傷亡數字，大家都要小心啲。」"},{"pid":"48e28194de42a2c8a788137f69615f33a09c6089","tid":826153,"uid":9812,"like":296,"dislike":8,"score":288,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:55:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾馬撚"},{"pid":"8041dd1a1715cb8a34da362a872e60d051bc6021","tid":826153,"uid":94828,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:09:47.000Z","msg":"乜水"},{"pid":"943bc02cc0d3751c38fe36d646facc244ed47bfc","tid":826153,"uid":21407,"like":729,"dislike":7,"score":722,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"上去收契妹"},{"pid":"bc45a4a9a1dcbe1bdfbcdb55baee833fcbadfc8b","tid":826153,"uid":51561,"like":667,"dislike":2,"score":665,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:11:07.000Z","msg":"佢係咪報埋Ocamp"},{"pid":"13f2ecd4033472d